ng Sequence","Stage 3","In the sequence shown below, tighten the crankcase bolts 1 to 8 to ","100°"," of bolt rotation using the ","service tool T3880105"," :","Crankcase Bolt 1 to 8 Tightening Sequence","T3880105 - Torque Angle Gauge","Perform the following operations:","Rotate the crankshaft clockwise. Check for tight spots and rectify as necessary.","Oil Pump - Installation","Sump - Installation","Camshaft Drive Chain Tensioner - Installation","Camshaft Cover - Installation","Clutch - Installation","Alternator Rotor - Installation","Engine - Installation"],"viewCount":5,"infoType":"InfoType09","views":[{"createdBy":"65a14134c48c038732ed6389","createdAt":"2024-01-18T14:47:25.059Z","_id":"65b238574e7861d9b70e6d1e"},{"createdBy":"65b4c751c20ee762078616c3","createdAt":"2024-01-18T14:46:30.166Z","_id":"65ba425f0cf8b13726664ff3"},{"createdBy":"643e47122b2ee15785df44e9","createdAt":"2024-03-07T11:20:06.332Z","_id":"65f2f05b673a4618e76aa92e"},{"createdBy":"643e47122b2ee15785df44e9","createdAt":"2024-03-07T11:20:06.332Z","_id":"65f30602673a4618e76d296f"},{"createdBy":"643e47122b2ee15785df44e9","createdAt":"2024-03-07T11:20:57.537Z","_id":"65f603f91de51b84d47229f2"}],"createdAt":"2024-01-18T12:24:05.621Z","updatedAt":"2024-03-16T20:41:29.029Z","__v":0,"updatedBy":"643e47122b2ee15785df44e9"}